<section class="about-me">
	<h1 class="section-title">About Me</h1>
	<div class="content">
		<p>
			I am Liuye Zhao, an undergraduate student majoring in Computer
			Science and Technology, Zhejiang University. I am now advised by
			Professor <a href="http://www.cad.zju.edu.cn/home/jin"
				>Xiaogang Jin</a
			>.
		</p>
		<p>
			My current research focuses on rendering <strong
				>related to deep learning</strong
			>, aiming to realize the visual world using physical simulation and
			deep learning. This work is highly valuable in creating 3D and even
			4D world models. Futhermore, I tend to explore various interesting
			rendering techniques that maximize rendering speed while ensuring
			high-quality visual effects. This work has significant applications
			in mobile rendering, film and television production, and animation.
		</p>
		<p>
			I am also interested in various geometric processing methods in
			computer graphics.
		</p>

		<p class="contact-line">
			<strong>Email:</strong> masterforliage@gmail.com
		</p>
		<p class="update-time">
			<em>Last updated: May 2026</em>
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

